Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:15.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\blur4}だから遠くまで歩き出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:28.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}ほかの誰も　僕や君になれるわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.98,0:22:34.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}失った輝きを二人で取り戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:37.20,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}俯いてる顔をあげた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:40.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}信じてみたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:42.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}不安ごと抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:47.21,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}確かなことはなにもない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:48.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:51.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}まだ冷えてゆく体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:54.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}嘘を一つ重ねる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:57.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}自分から逃げたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:22:58.85,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}目を閉じた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:01.89,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}一人じゃないから今
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.93,0:23:06.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}もっと遠くまで歩き出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:10.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}失うことも怖くはない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:13.03,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}染み付いた影がまた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:18.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}胸の内側を苦しめるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:28.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\blur4}これからは平気笑顔が溢れ出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:08.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}屹立於我們熱愛的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:15.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\blur4}邁向遙遠的彼方不再是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:28.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}無人能取代你我在彼此心中的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.98,0:22:34.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}讓我們一起奪回失去的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:37.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}告別灰心喪氣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:40.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}試著再相信一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:42.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}連同不安一起緊緊相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:47.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}一切都是這麼忐忑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:48.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:51.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}仍在逐漸變冷的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:54.26,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}陷入謊言的無限輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:57.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}不想再自我逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:22:58.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}閉上雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:01.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}不再孤身一人的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.93,0:23:06.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}能夠邁向地平線的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:10.15,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}不再害怕失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:13.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}揮之不去的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:18.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}依舊令內心痛苦難耐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:28.96,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\blur4}但是未來的我一定能重拾失去的笑容
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TXT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再不趕緊的話  就要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  滿大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您的關心  不過今天是週日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且現在已經是早上10點左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有課  現在也已經遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh  no  看我都做了什麼蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  回去再睡一會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺最近滿大小姐傻事越做越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅是滿大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該說她們是變得開朗了  還是不再迷惘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺和以前不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這果然是因為那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅僅是那兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐也很黏著他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小蒔也很喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自從風見先生來到這裡後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家變得開朗起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這明明是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可我卻無法坦率地高興起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是也改變一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想改變這種事能被允許嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去看電視吧  電視
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在浴缸裡連100都無法數到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有忍耐力的孩子越來越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可以說是「寬鬆教育」的弊端吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  又不是我喜歡才對自己寬鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要成為在浴缸裡能數到1萬的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能忍的女人事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2404
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2405
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2406
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2407
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2410
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸  飯菜要涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我說了那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道小幸的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,注意一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得去準備些新的冰塊才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我房間的冰箱裡有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蒔菜  來幫我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我能叫您小雄嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸  抱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  你沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,託大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們擔心了  真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼大事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請假？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什麼重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就快考試了他不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭考試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方還在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我拿下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,記得要好好複習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的內容會在考試裡出現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這個世界上會有考試這東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓考試消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,考試啊  考試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的話  讓考試消失也辦的到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  別說這種荒謬的事讓小幸困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是真的想要她那樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧  滿大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚飯做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來發生了這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後她就一直把自己關在房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手機也一直是電話留言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓考試消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滿說傻話已經是司空見慣的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照往常的話  幸也應該理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管的話  我想也不會出什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過之前發生過浴室那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我之後找幸談一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就交給風見君辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前有沒有聽說過僅僅想讓考試消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個女生便在學校裡放了火這個事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚  發生過這樣的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不知道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那件事  我就不問你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一件事希望你能明確地回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會讓小嶺同學做出什麼危險的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果發生那樣的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會全力安排好  讓幸和你們免受危害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和你之前的事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  到時希望你能助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了  由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必須成為好孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,記得告訴小嶺同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是沒法阻止考試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果阿幸還是沒來上課呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾天好像很累的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就可以放心了  滿大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被雄二叫過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被風見先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使想偷跑也是白費力氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您誤會了  我沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  叫我們過來的哥哥自己卻不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要不先離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是雄二還沒過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…都這麼晚了  不太安全吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不安全？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求求各位了  快點離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸你好像很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身體還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下午都請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有事瞞著我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟平時沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你太奇怪了  小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是快回宿舍…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了  你們快給我到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快  各位也快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  時間就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜點啦你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃  大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊逃到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來所有人都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在暑假前  整頓一下宿舍的紀律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是突然召集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位依然全部到場讓我感到很欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事在宿舍做不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  所有人都回宿舍去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  幸留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我收拾一下再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是太莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就交給風見我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  到底是搞什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這之後肯定會有少兒不宜的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸彈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經改造成倒數計時為0就停止運作了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以外行的水準來說這炸彈相當不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像嚇唬得有點過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了那個城市的  那個公園
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了啊  小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您終於想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我到周圍打聽了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很幸運碰到了你的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽他說你的父母遭遇了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家經營著一個小工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然生活艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是父母都非常疼愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可一旦工作繁忙起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們就沒空陪著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟風見先生相遇正好就是那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從您那寂寞的表情中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺到了跟自己相似的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟您在一起玩耍的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我忘記了寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  您漸漸地不再去那個公園了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後那一天  10歲的生日到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  今天是你的生日  我們就休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這些日子以來讓你那麼寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們決定今天一整天都陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼想慶祝生日你們兩個自己慶祝就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是在亂發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能原諒他們倆用寂寞兩個字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就概括了我忍受了那麼久的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我一個人在公園冷靜下來後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才發覺到自己說的話是那麼過份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了  什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽成了植物人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的任性  才讓他們遭遇事故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我必須做個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能乖乖聽話的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  我在那個城市也想起了一些自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  你有聽到我叫你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我當時有一點家庭煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心情很低落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過多虧了你任性地帶我瘋玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我心情好了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,任性有時也能幫助人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的師父也說過這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她說一句任性話都不懂說  太老實的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人看著就覺得心疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父母肯定也在你一直忍受著的痛苦裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想著孩子和工作究竟哪個重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最終他們得出了還是要把孩子放在第一的結論
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是你父母所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子的任性有時也會讓父母感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你再多任性一點也是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人努力到現在真是辛苦你了  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,師父還說過這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受恩不可恥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受恩不報才可恥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:19:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然那時的我被幸所拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那這次當是給她報恩就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在把你製作的炸彈引爆銷毀證據
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會被其他人發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經準備好了對策  把耳朵捂住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打雷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,煙火？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是為掩蓋爆炸聲而準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過看看煙火也挺不錯的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從那次事故之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一次都沒去探望過你母親對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為母親肯定憎恨著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可那天是你的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這鑰匙是你叔叔給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你生日快樂  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,致幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你10歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,願你的未來是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,願你可以永遠保持笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是將你的名字起為幸的我們的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愛對你來說可能還有點難理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就用這句話表達
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你生為我們的孩子  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這話該我說才對  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生說雖然不明顯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但確實有著恢復的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想以後多去探望一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以任性一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能請您擁抱我一分鐘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一分鐘就夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只要這點就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  世界樹的種子I
